description:
Plot.
The film tells the story of Peter (Christopher Denham) and Lorna (Nicole 
Vicius), a young Silver Lake couple, who attempt to infiltrate a cult and 
secretly film a documentary. At the center of the group is an enigmatic young 
woman named Maggie  (Brit Marling)  who claims to be from the year 2054 sent 
back in time in order to protect the chosen ones from the awful fate.Maggie 
never leaves her basement chamber, the members of the group follow Maggie 
blindly providing her organic food, obsessively cleaning the house, giving 
her their own blood for transfusions. But as the couple spend more and more 
time with Maggie and her believers, their relationship soon becomes strained 
Maggie begins to penetrate Peter emotionally, exposing a secret past that 
explains what brought him there in the first place.
